{"tid":2315442,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】【鋼鐵雄心IV】 香港人整嘅香港mod接近完成，有少少地方需要大家幫手","createTime":"2020-12-07T07:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T18:39:46.000Z","uid":227929,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bc722ec1032732ea62f9e01f4de1b390f7da67ee","tid":2315442,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的，HOI4本身無香港呢個地方玩，所以有個巴打決定自己整屬於自己嘅香港mod<br />\n<br />\n1936 年港督郝德傑<br />\n仲有整咗hoi4嘅香港地圖同省份（state）<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/25/raBzWI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2FraBzWI.png&h=51091461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFocus Tree<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/25/qxwKEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2FqxwKEr.png&h=f9ef8446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/25/fc5SmP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2Ffc5SmP.png&h=75364994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/25/F2ZOt3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2FF2ZOt3.png&h=c12f44e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家仲寫緊虛構線嘅國策，希望大家可以比啲idea講下點寫<br />\n<br />\n暫時虛構線會係講香港淪陷 英屬香港政府遷往轉福克蘭成立新香港，主要係會寫當地發展同埋重奪香港<br />\n<br />\n另一條虛構線就係講大粵民國嘅<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係作者只係helper"},{"pid":"cc66a380ed4769be4ea5c9c21644bc0145dae258","tid":2315442,"uid":227929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"太古船塢<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/25/T9IuLM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2FT9IuLM.png&h=0010a224&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6162d2f728d96fd5841c15589df80fe8e9ab151b","tid":2315442,"uid":233905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:00:4